data.description: Charming and updated home in the Heart of Katy! Featuring a newly painted interior, new ceiling fans, new blinds, new recessed lighting, newer roof, newer hot water heater and freshened up landscaping. Large Bonus Room/Den that can be used many different ways. Expansive backyard features a new fence on two sides and mature trees that provide lots of shade. Zoned to excellent Katy ISD schools, walk to Mary Jo Peckham Park to enjoy trails, a fishing pond, playground, gym, pool and group classes (free for Katy residents). Refrigerator, washer & dryer included. No HOA, No MUD taxes! Ready for move in!
